dct_title_s: Railroad and county map of New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Shows railroads and unfinished railroads, state capitol, county seats and post offices; railroads outlined in colors. Relief shown by hachures. Inset: Environs of Hudson County. From: Cram's bankers' and brokers' railroad atlas ... Chicago : Geo. F. Cram, 1885.
dct_publisher_sm: Chicago : Geo. F. Cram, engraver and publisher, [c1885]
